data.description: Amazing Split plan, ideal for entertaining. Fully Loaded with beautiful upgrades and finishes from the stair rails to the wood floors and light fixtures, this property has it all! Primary Bedroom is on the main level, with sitting area and oversized closet, dual sinks and so much more! Upstairs offers a large game room with built-in surround sound and a wet bar complete with mini fridge and separate sitting area and 3 additional bedrooms. The back yard is right off the living area with an elevated covered patio overlooking you private oasis! You're going to love this home! Schedule your viewing and make your Offer!
